{"tid":2258927,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中華英雄】胡兵飾演新版華英雄　網民大讚造型正過鄭伊健","createTime":"2020-10-26T12:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:55:33.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e32cb283e61c1c230d8b15dfaf87e75c34811c5","tid":2258927,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"眾所周知胡兵是型男一名，身高達1.89米的他原來已年近50歲，保養得宜完全不見歲月痕跡。近日他飾演「華英雄」的造型照流出，比伊健的版本多了份滄桑感，但論有型靚仔絕不遜於對方，難怪網民激讚。<br />\n<br />\n電影講述華英雄在美國唐人街，團結起一眾華人，奮勇戰鬥，力克宿敵，傳承中華文化的熱血英雄傳奇，聽落跟1999年版本分別相當大，相信不會出現吳鎮宇飾演的反派「無敵」。不過，對於一眾原著迷來說，最貼近漫畫版華英雄的演員，要數90年代初何家勁的版本，至今仍叫人津津樂道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMTFsbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMTFsbf.jpg&h=0839497c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKmvPpB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKmvPpB.jpg&h=ff7f064c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bR7RCW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bR7RCW.jpg&h=d9c4776b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VskP4XX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVskP4XX.jpg&h=826618c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DukAf4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDukAf4C.jpg&h=ec402d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMvP4XY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMvP4XY.jpg&h=086e1256&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L9xihZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L9xihZ.jpg&h=7f5c2ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tXYaPpF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtXYaPpF.jpg&h=6339cb08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"664d657eb1f072c854ee1cc51423e174edf79c6b","tid":2258927,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202